        <updateDate>2018-03-15T19:32:39Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Combating the Opioid Epidemic Act</strong></p> <p>This bill amends the 21st Century Cures Act to provide additional funds through FY2027 for&nbsp;state grants to&nbsp;address the opioid abuse crisis.</p> <p>The bill provides funds to the Department of Health and Human Services through FY2022 for state grants to conduct research on addiction and pain related to substance misuse.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
